<h1 class="ptitle">FOREST</h1>
<br />
The fight was over. 
The only sounds were the sharp crackle of the fire and the frantic breathing of the woman clutching the broken chair leg in her hands.
<br /><br />
You lowered your weapon, scanning the room — and that’s when you noticed movement. A glimpse, just for a second, of wide, terrified eyes peeking out from behind the corner of a closet door.
<br /><br />
The daughter.
